data.description: Embrace the charm of this wonderful 3-bed, 2.5-bath haven adorned with solar panels and a 3-car garage! Come inside & fall in love with the fabulous interior featuring wood-look & tile flooring, an open den/office, and a bright living room with soaring ceilings. Share lasting memories in the large great room offering sliding glass doors that open to the back patio. The kitchen displays recessed lighting, cabinetry with crown moulding, built-in appliances, and a center island that adds to the counter space. Head upstairs to discover a HUGE loft perfect for an additional living area. Large main bedroom provides an ensuite with two vanities, make-up desk, and a walk-in closet. Finally, the expansive backyard has a relaxing covered patio for unwinding. This rare find will sell fast!
